# Upstream Go-module CVEs in noble's go.mod that we can't patch without
# forking noble. Each entry lists the vulnerable package, the installed
# version, and the upstream fix version. Expiry triggers a re-triage —
# by then noble (currently v11.4.0 / chain-id noble-1) may have bumped
# these deps.

